.TH WC 1 "14 Dec 2025" neocore
.
.SH NAME
wc \- display words, lines, bytes and chars count
.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B wc
[\fI\,OPTION\/\fR]...
[\fI\,FILES\/\fR]...
.br
.
.SH DESCRIPTION
Display words, lines, bytes and chars count.
.PP
If no files specified stdin used for an input. If as file specified "-"
.B wc
will use stdin.
.PP
If no options specified display lines, words and bytes count.
.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-c, \-\-bytes
display bytes count
.TP
\fB\-l, \-\-lines
display lines count
.TP
\fB\-m, \-\-chars
display chars count
.TP
\fB\-w, \-\-words
display words count
.TP
\fB\-\-help\fR
display help message and exit
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
print version and exit
.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
\fB0\fR
sucess
.TP
\fB1\fR
an error occurred
.
